      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>式微式微，胡不歸？微君之故，胡為乎中露？
式微式微，胡不歸？微君之躬，胡為乎泥中？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>1 Reduced ! Reduced !
Why not return ?
If it were not for your sake, 0 prince,
How should we be thus exposed to the dew ?

2 Reduced ! reduced !
Why not return ?
If it were not for your person, 0 prince；,
How should we be here in the mire ?</seg>
      </tuv>
